cu.explanation_en: Setting the local SCTP data port to an out-of-range value of 99999 will cause SCTP connection failures and prevent F1 interface establishment.

du.explanation_en: Setting the PRACH configuration index to an invalid value of 999 will cause random access configuration errors and prevent UE initial access.
du.explanation_zh: 將 PRACH 配置索引設定為無效值 999 會導致隨機接入配置錯誤，並阻止 UE 初始接入。
